== 剧情 ==
该剧讲述以“老何”为代表的[[警察|中华人民共和国警察]]的光辉形象。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2008-05/09/content_8134162.htm|title=资料：电视剧《警察故事》剧情梗概|accessdate=2014-03-07|date=2008-05-09|work=新华网|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081006140143/http://news.xinhuanet.com/ent/2008-05/09/content_8134162.htm|archivedate=2008-10-06}}</ref>

